Package com.launchdarkly.sdk.server.integrations Description

This package provides a DynamoDB-backed data store for the LaunchDarkly Java SDK.

For more details about how and why you can use a persistent data store, see: https://docs.launchdarkly.com/sdk/features/storing-data/dynamodb#java

For details on usage, see DynamoDb.
